These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Flower: iris, azalea
1. Flower:iris is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Flower   | azalea | iris |

 #################################
 
